            <p class="font-weight-normal">ABP为现代Web应用程序提供了全栈的开发模型和基础设施.</p>        </div>
        <div class="row pb-5">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="p-4">
                    <img class="subsection-icon mb-3" src="assets/icons/1-modular.png" />
                    <h3 class="text-primary display-6">模块化架构</h3>
                    <p class="font-weight-normal">模块化设计,可从底到顶进行延伸.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="p-4">
                    <img class="subsection-icon mb-3" src="assets/icons/2-micro.png" />
                    <h3 class="text-primary display-6">聚焦微服务</h3>
                    <p class="font-weight-normal">支持微服务架构有助于构建自主微服务.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="p-4">
                    <img class="subsection-icon mb-3" src="assets/icons/3-ddd.png" />
                    <h3 class="text-primary display-6">领域驱动设计</h3>
                    <p class="font-weight-normal">根据DDD模式和原则设计和开发.为应用程序提供分层模型.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row pb-5">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="p-4">
                    <img class="subsection-icon mb-3" src="assets/icons/4-autho.png" />
